2005-01-19
	* changelog started
	* main changes from release 0.8.12 wich I remember:
		- support for UUID
		- created application layer
		- created data layer (multi db support)
		- multilanguage support
		- multidomain support
		- some new tabs
		
2005-03-02
	* default values for domain depending options separated from main config 
	  file		

2005-04-20
	* rewrited user and admin interface to use application layer
	* added XXL support
	
2005-05-20
	* consolidated config files
	* fixed few bugs
	* changed default charset to utf-8
	* finished rewriting application logic to use application layer
	
2005-06-28
	* serweb 0.9.3 released
	
2005-07-08
	* support for creating modules
	* authentication functions moved to auth module
	* created modules auth_radius and auth_ldap

2005-07-18
	* fixed bug: "Use of undefined constant PEAR_LOG_INFO" when logging 
	  is disabled

2005-07-19
	* apu_speed_dial - added ability to export information about sorting direction to smarty

2005-07-20
	* fixed look of login screen in IE
	* added czech and dutch translation
	* added scripts which should help with debuging of php configuration
	* support to specify charset of sended emails

2005-07-25
	* added ability to change first name, last name and phone of subscriber

2005-08-10
	* created script for generation internationalized images of buttons

2005-08-20
	* modularized
		
2005-08-29
	* support for postgesql
	* fixed highlight of selected tab user_preferences in admin interface
	
2005-09-01
	* removed unused type of user preference 'list of providers'
	* fixed bug "undefined function get_acc_entries" in some configuration case

2005-09-02
	* fixed used preferences in order to display radio buttons

2005-09-19
	* fixed security issue: the click2dial applet works without authentication.

2006-01-11	
	* rewrited classes from phplib (Auth, Perms and session management)
	* domain management support (tabs domains and customers in admin interface)
	* user attributes expanded by domain attrs and global attrs
	* users are now indexed by uid. Indexing by username@domain is no more supported
	* addapted to new database structure
	* added possibility to register user by admin
	* added possibility to disable requiring confirmation of registration


	* UIDs are displayed in list of subscribers in admin interface	
	* updated interface for URI editing
	* added possibility to assign admin to domain
	* added checks if IMAP extension is installed	
	* "server monitoring" removed
	* "caller screening" removed
	* rewrited ACL module to use user_attrs instead of group table
	
	
	* added per-domain customization
	* support for XML-RPC Ser interface
	
2006-11-28
	* serweb now should work with PHP 5.x and Runkit extension

2006-12-07
	* min and max value of int attribute can be specified
	 
2006-12-20
	* similar attributes could be grouped together
2007-01-18
	* page for edit attribute types improved - sorting and filtering feature added
2007-02-05
	* lists of users are sortable
2007-02-06
	* list of customers is sortable

